creator: Anoniem
description:
LibriVox recording of Ali Baba en de veertig roovers by Anoniem. (Translated by J. W. Gerhard.)
Read in Dutch by Marcel Coenders

Ali Baba vindt een schat van roovers en neemt een deel van de schat weg. Uiteraard willen de roovers wraak nemen. - Summary by Marcel Coenders

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

Download M4B (51MB)
